OL,3,C100 extra officers to tackle
OL,4,Cantisemitism in London
OL,6,FThe Metropolitan Police has announced
OL,7,Fa community protection team of 100
OL,8,Fextra officers to help safeguard the
OL,9,FJewish community, despite the force's
OL,10,Fchief previously saying 300 more
OL,11,Fofficers were needed to tackle the
OL,12,Frise in antisemitism across the
OL,13,Fcapital.
OL,15,FThe force said in its initial phase,
OL,16,Fthe new team will be "primarily
OL,17,Ffocused on protecting the Jewish
OL,18,Fcommunity, which faces some of the
OL,19,Fhighest levels of hate crime alongside
OL,20,Fsignificant terrorist and hostile
OL,21,Fstate threats".
OL,26,@xD@VOU}D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
