OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1778087158
OL,3,C100 extra officers to tackle
OL,4,Cantisemitism in London
OL,6,FIt added that it would bring together
OL,7,F"neighbourhood policing, specialist
OL,8,Fprotection and counter terrorism
OL,9,Fcapabilities" to provide a "more
OL,10,Fvisible, intelligenceled and
OL,11,Fcoordinated presence focused on
OL,12,Fprotecting Jewish communities across
OL,13,FLondon".
OL,15,FSince late March, there have been a
OL,16,Fseries of arson attacks at Jewish
OL,17,Fsites in London, as well as a double
OL,18,Fstabbing in Golders Green that is
OL,19,Fbeing treated as an act of terrorism.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@MO]qD@\OUuD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
