OL,3,C100 extra officers to tackle
OL,4,Cantisemitism in London
OL,6,FMetropolitan Police Commissioner Sir
OL,7,FMark Rowley previously said 300 extra
OL,8,Fpolice officers were needed across
OL,9,FLondon as he warned of a growing
OL,10,F"pandemic" of antisemitism in the UK.
OL,12,FCounter-terrorism police are
OL,13,Finvestigating a suspected arson at a
OL,14,Fformer synagogue in Nelson Street,
OL,15,FWhitechapel, in the early hours of
OL,16,FTuesday.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1778087158
OL,3,C100 extra officers to tackle
OL,4,Cantisemitism in London
OL,6,FA Met Police spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"British Jews now appear on the hate
OL,8,Flists of every major extremist
OL,9,Fmovement: extreme rightwing groups,
OL,10,FIslamist terrorists, elements of the
OL,11,Fextreme left and hostile state actors.
OL,13,F"It is a deeply concerning
OL,14,Fconvergence, and Jewish communities
OL,15,Fare living with the consequences of
OL,16,Fthat risk daily.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1778087158
OL,3,C100 extra officers to tackle
OL,4,Cantisemitism in London
OL,6,F"This focus does not mean the
OL,7,FMetropolitan Police is deprioritising
OL,8,Fother communities. Hate crime in all
OL,9,Fits forms ` including ongoing efforts
OL,10,Fto tackle racism, antiMuslim hate
OL,11,Fcrime, homophobia and other forms of
OL,12,Fhatred in the capital ` remains a core
OL,13,Fpolicing priority."
OL,15,FThe Home Office is backing the Met's
OL,16,Faction with #18 million, and a further
OL,17,F#4 million will be made available
OL,18,Fthrough the Jewish Community
OL,19,FProtective Security Grant to help
OL,20,Fsupport community-led and charity work.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
