CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1778087158
OL,3,C100 extra officers to tackle
OL,4,Cantisemitism in London
OL,6,F"We will do everything in our power to
OL,7,Frid society of the evil of
OL,8,Fantisemitism," Home Secretary Shabana
OL,9,FMahmood said.
OL,11,FAt the same time, England and Wales's
OL,12,Fchief prosecutor has issued fresh
OL,13,Fguidance in an effort to fast-track
OL,14,Fhate crime prosecutions.
OL,16,FDirector of public prosecutions (DPP)
OL,17,FStephen Parkinson told the Press
OL,18,FAssociation he hoped to "put a line in
OL,19,Fthe sand" and stop an "uptick" in
OL,20,Fantisemitic behaviour.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@NO]zD@YOU{D@IO]{D@WOU{D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1778087158
OL,3,C100 extra officers to tackle
OL,4,Cantisemitism in London
OL,6,F"It seems there is a pattern of
OL,7,Fcopycat antisemitism taking place," he
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,FIssuing the new guidance, Mr Parkinson
OL,11,Ftold prosecutors that "any supporting
OL,12,Fevidence can be obtained subsequently"
OL,13,Fonce the evidential threshold for a
OL,14,Fcharge is met.
OL,16,FAnd Sir Keir on Tuesday hosted a
OL,17,Froundtable of senior figures from the
OL,18,Fpolice, the arts, higher education,
OL,19,Ftrade unions and businesses.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@cO]sD@WOUtD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1778087158
OL,3,C100 extra officers to tackle
OL,4,Cantisemitism in London
OL,6,FHe said universities will be expected
OL,7,Fto "demonstrate action" to tackle
OL,8,Fantisemitism among students, as part
OL,9,Fof a "zero tolerance" approach on
OL,10,Fcampuses.
OL,12,FThe Arts Council will also be expected
OL,13,Fto withdraw funding and claw it back
OL,14,Ffrom anyone who is found to promote
OL,15,Fantisemitism.
OL,17,FTurning to potential foreign backers
OL,18,Fof antisemitic attacks, Sir Keir said
OL,19,Fthe Government was "fast-tracking
OL,20,Flegislation to tackle these malign
OL,21,Fthreats".
OL,26,@oD@DOUoD@WO]qD@FOUqD@UO]{D@TOU}D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1778087158
OL,3,C100 extra officers to tackle
OL,4,Cantisemitism in London
OL,6,FHe said: "One of the lines of inquiry
OL,7,Fis whether a foreign state has been
OL,8,Fbehind some of these incidents.
OL,10,F"We are investigating, of course, all
OL,11,Fthe possibilities.
OL,13,F"And we are clear that these actions
OL,14,Fwill have consequences if that proves
OL,15,Fto be the case.
OL,17,F"Our message to Iran or to any other
OL,18,Fcountry that might seek to foment
OL,19,Fviolence, hatred or division in
OL,20,Fsociety is that it will not be
OL,21,Ftolerated."
OL,26,@nD@JOUrD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOU}D@KO]
